responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "1D0660CE4EA1BB7CDBEB3886A5324EAB", "Long and far in the murk and dark of Riverlands, a Priestess of Pain did hunger and lurk. She wandered through the mud, stepping into muck, looking for food not of the likes of normal ones. Cackling out spells and cracking brittle bones, she decided to explore and roam. Step, step, stepping from muck to village road, she spied a hut of adults and wee ones. Knock, knock, knock! A rap upon the door. Pa and Mum thrown to the floor, and wee ones eaten one by one. A hunger for more, and off did she go, village by village, eating them up whole!")
name: MADD_0007_TOF_Read_PriestessAndThePiper_6
